<component type="desktop">
  <id>io.mimiri.notes</id>
  <name>Mimiri Notes</name>
  <summary>Secure Device-Synchronized Notepad</summary>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">io.mimiri.notes.desktop</launchable>

  <metadata_license>FSFAP</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-2.0-only</project_license>

	<description>
		<p>
			A secure, open-source notepad for your confidential notes, credentials, and sensitive data with end-to-end encryption and real-time synchronization across all your devices.
		</p>
		<p>Key features:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>End-to-end encryption with AES-GCM-256 to protect your data before it leaves your device</li>
			<li>Real-time synchronization across all platforms</li>
			<li>Hierarchical organization with unlimited nesting of notes</li>
			<li>Collaborative sharing of encrypted notes with trusted contacts</li>
			<li>Complete version history to track and restore previous versions</li>
			<li>Offline access with local encrypted cache</li>
			<li>Password masking for sensitive text</li>
			<li>No tracking - your data stays private</li>
		</ul>
		<p>
			All data is encrypted client-side before transmission. The open-source codebase (GPLv2) ensures transparent security with features like automatic locking, secure password fields, and a recycle bin for accidental deletions.
		</p>
	</description>

